{"tid":2102684,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【炒股】 你人生輸得最勁果獲，係點？？？？","createTime":"2020-07-10T15:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T15:35:58.000Z","uid":6783,"like":43,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"78b5d2c0b8d2838d52c2eea6b1cd1701c315fb5b","tid":2102684,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"有一日朝早，<br />\n大概 9:15 左右，就快開市 <br />\n我係床上半睡半醒，拎起部手機，<br />\n望下琴晚道指走勢，睇下新聞 headline，<br />\n迅速分析一下環球經濟走勢 <br />\n然後揀左隻近牛，大概 0.05 果d 價位，開市即入<br />\n大概買左1萬hkd <br />\n<br />\n點知，一開市無耐就跌到0.04 <br />\n心諗：「正呀，溝多手先」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後，買多2萬hkd 去溝貨 <br />\n<br />\n再隔多陣，屌你，跌到去 0.03 <br />\n哈，咪本多終勝囉，驚西咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買多2萬 hkd <br />\n呢個 moment total 買左5萬蚊貨 <br />\n<br />\n仆街，隔多陣跌到去 0.018 左右 <br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">我失控  !!!! 唔忿氣 !!!!! 好撚想追數 !!!!!!   </span></strong></span><br />\n大注屌多5萬落去溝貨<br />\nTotal 手持10萬蚊貨 <br />\n<br />\n再隔多陣，0.015 .... 0.013 .... 0.010 ... <br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">隻牛死撚左呀屌你老母 !!!!!! </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個 moment 終於係床上訓醒左 ，<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">我呆撚左 </span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>10皮野，咁就冇左 !?  </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>開始傻笑，「哈？」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>個世界好似停撚左咁</strong>"},{"pid":"f3fc94b3c425de9f435545f8c25b850a748aef52","tid":2102684,"uid":5278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:55:37.000Z","msg":"又開?"},{"pid":"a303b5777f8593ac1c3683bdad2efe21974ffd3e","tid":2102684,"uid":270237,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">港共越係唔想我投<br />\n我越係要去投</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">港共越係唔想我投<br />\n我越係要去投</